name: Elena Salsa
description: I’m very easy to get along with, I love to laugh and have fun. I am very passionate, and secure in who I am. I respect people and want to be respected. I love to be showered with attention. I love going out and dancing and enjoying the person I am with.I’m open-hearted girl who likes to take everything that life can offer but to give in return as well! I am active and enthusiastic, I am cheerful and I treat people just I want them to treat me. I am attentive and caring; I need to love and to be loved, to bring my future man happiness and joy. I don’t like to sit on one place and I am dreaming of strong and friendly family. I am ready to have serious relationship and I am ready to start with a man that knows how to make a woman happy…
